data.description:
Charming, fantastic home in a great location! Pride of ownership evident in every corner and lovingly
maintained. Enjoy vintage charm with updated and modern amenities including updated kitchen and bathroom. Large living room with plenty of space to also have a front coffee corner taking in the morning light. Basement has extensive storage areas and not one but two bonus rooms that could be converted to a third and fourth bedroom. Or they could be used as a home office, home gym, rec room- the options are endless! This wonderful home has everything you need including room to grow. Backyard is fully fenced with privacy
and great for entertaining. Rare large two car garage. Enjoy demanded area with easy access to bus and light rail systems. This home is a can't miss!
